{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"To increase the chance of placing high-priority labels on the map, you can"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provide an array of "},{"code":"textAnchor","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" locations, each paired with an offset value."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"The renderer will attempt to place the label at each location, in order, before"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"moving on to the next location+offset. Use "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textJustify: auto"},{"text":" to choose","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"justification based on anchor position.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSExpression","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSExpression"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"text":"textVariableAnchorOffset","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The length of the array must be even, and must alternate between enum and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"point entries. i.e., each anchor location must be accompanied by a point, and","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"that point defines the offset when the corresponding anchor location is used.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Positive offset values indicate right and down, while negative values indicate"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"left and up. Anchor locations may repeat, allowing the renderer to try multiple"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"offsets to try and place a label using the same anchor.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When present, this property takes precedence over "},{"code":"textAnchor","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textVariableAnchor"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textOffset"},{"text":", and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textRadialOffset"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"json","type":"codeListing","code":["{ \"text-variable-anchor-offset\": [\"top\", [0, 4], \"left\", [3,0], \"bottom\", [1,","1]] } "]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"When the renderer chooses the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"top"},{"type":"text","text":" anchor, "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"[0, 4]"},{"type":"text","text":" will be used for"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textOffset"},{"text":"; the text will be shifted down by 4 ems.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"When the renderer chooses the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"left"},{"text":" anchor, ","type":"text"},{"code":"[3, 0]","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" will be used for"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"textOffset","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"; the text will be shifted right by 3 ems.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This property is only applied to the style if "},{"code":"text","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is non-","type":"text"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"symbolPlacement"},{"type":"text","text":" is set to an expression that evaluates to or"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"MLNSymbolPlacementPoint"},{"text":". Otherwise, it is ignored.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can set this property to an expression containing any of the following:"}],"type"